Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with using drones equipped with cameras for 3D scanning. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses an automatic method for generating drone trajectories. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper mentions a quantitative evaluation using a photorealistic video game simulator. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is relevant as the paper deals with scene geometry and trajectory planning. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions using a mathematical model of scene coverage and leveraging the submodularity property extensively to design the trajectory planning algorithm.
